    "cars_per_year": "Est. 1,230,000",
    "acres": "Est. 0.85",
    "note": "Russell Speeder's Car Wash & Shell Station in 1429 East Putnam Avenue, Old Greenwich, CT 06870 with asking price $20,000,000, sales/revenue $2,688,000, EBITDA $4,000,000, Cars/Yr Est. 1,230,000. Use this as a structured lead and verify important numbers before making a decision.",
